Hello, every pony, its Sean.M  
againAnd here comes the seasons of winter, a beautiful season for all ponykind
 
So let me present the first gift for the snowflake season
 
「Canterlot Royal Ballet Academy Series Winter Suite」 
Also named as “The Diamond music box”
 
It’s a suite series collect of many different kind of music I created for this winter, most of them are BGM, and based on Ballet music. 
And I also present it, with this new artwork together
 
I’m not very good at drawing griffin, but I took it as a challenge. 
And this is the result, it took me almost 4 days, but still anyway, it’s worth to try.
 
Gilda and Gabby dancing this “Galcier fairy”
 
Gilda's dress were tribute to "Frozen", i think you can saw that, the light blue dresses with the light green mixing , create the color like polar light. 
and the short tutu said that the ballet dress she weared are classic type, she also wearing a pretty silk cape with snowflake on it. i think she is really cute wearing that.
 
and Gabby's dress are some kind of japanese children anime's style,kind of like some dress also fit Pinkiepie . and the long skirt are showing that her ballet dress is Romantic type, and with the Mymelody's mark on her pink tights, kind of childesh and lovely.
 
this commission are deal with 40USD, and if you need commission, please note me anytime ,thank you. 
 
hope you like this artwork, thank you.
 
Sean.M 
COMMISSION RULE==  
"Royal Canterlot ballet sereis" are major, but you can ask for other subject too 
‧- no limit taken number   
‧- working date within 5 days  
‧- with background and high quality render  
‧- general charge are 30 dollars USD, and the clinet can see the result to descide how much you willing to pay, over 35 USD will give bonus artwork
